overview:
We would like to introduce itself as a pre Eminent Manufacturers, Order Suppliers & Exporters of fine quality Gem stones.

We owe our success to our primary objective -Customer Delight and Satisfaction by providing the Best Quality of Precious & Semiprecious Loose Gemstones Beads, Cabochon, Cut Gemstone Beads, Chips, UN-Cut Beads,Sterling Silver Jewelry etc!!

Gems Creation has been serving the gem and jewelry industry for the last 25 years.

We are located in the heart of Jaipur city. Gems Creation was established with a vision to satisfy customer requirements through its quality.

We have been in this field for four generations so we have a vast experience in this trade.

You can be completely assured of Reliable Quality,Finish & inexplicable Luster at unmatched Prices because you are buying directly from the manufacturers.
